H. H. MOTTER, Collector of Internal Revenue for the District of Kansas, v. Otto THEIS. No. 1449. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. July 6, 1936. S. S. Alexander, U. S. Atty., of Topeka, Kan., for appellant. Foulston, Siefkin, Foulston & Morris, of Wichita, Kan., for appellee.

Before LEWIS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellant.
